## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sampleprof/profilesymbollist">ProfileSymbolList</a> records the list of function symbols shown up in the binary used to generate the profile.

It is useful to to discriminate a function being so cold as not to shown up in the profile and a function newly added.
